  "prompt": "How can I get job in Accenture?",
  "response": "To get a job at Accenture, follow these steps:\n\n1. Preparation\n- Research Accenture and understand their business\n- Update your resume highlighting relevant skills\n- Build a strong LinkedIn profile\n\n2. Qualification Requirements\n- Bachelor's or Master's degree in relevant field\n- Good academic performance\n- Technical skills (depending on role)\n- Strong communication skills\n- Basic programming knowledge (for technical roles)\n\n3. Application Process\n- Visit Accenture careers website\n- Create a profile\n- Search and apply for suitable job openings\n- Fill out online application carefully\n- Upload updated resume\n\n4. Recruitment Stages\n- Online application screening\n- Online aptitude/technical test\n- Technical interview\n- HR interview\n- Final interview\n\n5. Skill Development\n- Learn in-demand technical skills\n- Develop soft skills\n- Practice problem-solving\n- Stay updated with industry trends\n\n6. Campus Recruitment\n- Participate in campus placement drives\n- Attend Accenture recruitment events\n- Prepare for campus interviews\n\n7. Referral\n- Network with Accenture employees\n- Ask for referrals\n- Attend job fairs and professional events\n\n8. Additional Tips\n- Showcase leadership qualities\n- Demonstrate adaptability\n- Be confident during interviews",
